  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "お客様のリクエストに応じてペットを捕まえ、育て、レンタルすることでペットショップを管理しましょう。通信ケーブルを使ってペットを交換したり、対戦したりすることができます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Similar to its predecessor, this is an animal-raising RPG adding more animals and improvements.\n\nThe protagonist's father, who runs a pet shop, goes missing after a shipwreck. The protagonist takes over the pet shop management and embarks on an adventure with her exceptional pets to find clues about her father's whereabouts.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The player manages the requests of customers who visit the pet shop.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ],
